data.description: Terrific value on a home in a great area of town priced to sell with fully owned solar making for a nearly non-existent electric bill.  Oversized, gated RV parking with both 30 & 50 AMP electric hookups & water and a huge backyard you can drive around to with storage shed, existing structure to create fabric covered boat parking and tons & tons of space to add an additional, massive garage, pool, casita or possibly all three.  Home is well maintained and has recently painted exterior, recently overhauled HVAC system, Solar and located in a great quiet south side neighborhood.  This property is fantastic & offers 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, galley kitchen with newer appliances, generously sized dining room and living room, enclosed AZ room with wall storage AND a bonus hidden storage or safe room behind.  Abundant additional storage exists throughout for a home of this size. Extended rear covered patio runs the entire length of the home. This home offers so much & is priced exceptionally well. Home has been loved by current (senior) couple w/ some physical restrictions.  We LOVE this home & know you will too.
